<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>Who is the Winner of the LinkedIn Acquisition? Hint: It"s Not Microsoft or LinkedIn</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Who is the Winner of the LinkedIn Acquisition? Hint: It's Not Microsoft or LinkedIn" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/1409685364-microsoft-accidentally-teases-windows-9-quickly-deletes-post.jpg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
